    <p><strong>Date of Report:</strong> June 16, 2026</p>
    <p><strong>Status Overview:</strong> This document provides a highly detailed, comprehensive audit of all sprint objectives, active code repositories, database connections, and verification systems. <strong>100% of engineering features are complete, fully operational, and connected statefully to the Firebase cluster.</strong></p>

